            </tr>
            <tr>
               <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>007</strong></td>
               <td vAlign="top" colspan="8" align="left">ou<br><em>[Item is a kit (007/00)]</em></td>
            </tr>
         </table>
   </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Field length</strong> - For the category of material <strong>kit</strong>, field 007 should consist of two
                     character positions.
      </div>
